      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:1:157:2",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/1/157/2",
      "text": [
        "الْحَمْدُ للهِ الَّذِي جَعَلَ الْحَمْدَ مِفْتَاحاً لِذِكْرِهِ، وَسَبَباً لِلْمَزِيدِ مِنْ فَضْلِهِ، وَدَلِيلاً عَلَى آلاَئِهِ وَعَظَمَتِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "Praise be to Allāh who made praise the Key for His remembrance, a means for increase of His bounty and a guide for His Attributes and Dignity."
        ]
      }
    }
  },
